[gd_scene load_steps=3 format=3]

; Dev-only greybox for the task-11 manual playtest (F6). The driver builds a generated Bank mission
; from a fixed seed on _ready (MissionGenerator.build → MissionController realizes floors/guards/
; obstacles/loot/drops/escape + spawns the player). Walk it: slip past a cone, pick/keycard the vault
; gate, bag loot → a Drop Point, then Escape to end the mission. See docs/tasks/11_mission_generation.md.

